text: Anthony Thomas Aquinas Carmona, SC, ORTT (born March 7, 1953) is a Trinidadian politician. He was the fifth President of Trinidad and Tobago. He became president in 2013, and left office in 2018. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Trinidad and Tobago Category:University of the West Indies alumni
